'''野性妹網'''（'''Girls Gone Wild''', '''GGW'''），是在1997年，由{{link-en|乔·法蘭斯|Joe Francis|}}，於[[美國|美國]][[加州|加州]][[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]（總部）成立一家色情網站<ref name="NYT">{{cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2004/04/04/style/the-very-long-legs-of-girls-gone-wild.html?pagewanted=all&src=pm |title=超級長腿的《野性妹網》（英文版） |author=Mireya Navarro |date=2004年4月4日 |publisher=紐約時報 |accessdate=2012年12月2日 |archive-date=2020年11月12日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112021052/http://www.nytimes.com/2004/04/04/style/the-very-long-legs-of-girls-gone-wild.html?pagewanted=all&src=pm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

它主要業務是在美國各大洲省份，經營最早是由[[直銷市場廣告性|直銷市場廣告性]]，擴展至[[資訊型廣告|資訊型廣告]]方式經營色情拍攝<ref name="VT">{{cite web |url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117876991 |title=「性」王之王（英文版） |author=Michael Schneider |date=2002年12月8日 |publisher=Variety |accessdate=2012年10月2日 |archive-date=2019年6月30日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190630233426/https://variety.com/2002/tv/news/wild-informercial-struts-its-stuff-1117876991/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。它在拍攝成人電影作品，已達至200多部電影。但经常官司缠身，包括不正当销售<ref name="FTC">{{cite web |url=http://www.ftc.gov/opa/2003/12/girlsgonewild.shtm |title=Sellers of ‘Girls Gone Wild’ Videos Charged with Deceptive Practices |date=17 December 2003 |publisher=Federal Trade Commission |accessdate=3 October 2012 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120214015818/http://www.ftc.gov/opa/2003/12/girlsgonewild.shtm |archivedate=2012-02-14}}</ref> 
2004年，GGW决定以1100万美元对乱收费一案达成庭外和解。<ref name="FTC2">{{cite web |url=http://www.ftc.gov/opa/2004/07/girlsgonewild.shtm |title=Sellers of ‘Girls Gone Wild’ Videos to Pay $1.1 Million to Settle Charges of Unauthorized Shipping and Billing |date=30 July 2004 |publisher=Federal Trade Commission |accessdate=3 October 2012 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120728095620/http://www.ftc.gov/opa/2004/07/girlsgonewild.shtm |archivedate=2012-07-28}}</ref><ref name="TMZ">{{cite web |url=http://www.tmz.com/2008/03/19/ashley-dupre-gone-wild-legal-or-jailbait/ |title=Ashley Dupre Gone "Wild"-- Legal or Jailbait? |date=19 March 2008 |publisher=TMZ |accessdate=3 October 2012 |archive-date=2012-03-30 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66Y5nhcTl?url=http://www.tmz.com/2008/03/19/ashley-dupre-gone-wild-legal-or-jailbait/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="FINDLAW2">{{cite web |url=http://news.findlaw.com/hdocs/docs/spitzer/dupreggw42808cmp.html |title=Ashley Alexandra Dupre, the Former Prostitute Who Had a Paid Liasion With Ex-N.Y. Governor Eliot Spitzer Files a $10M Lawsuit Against Girls Gone Wild |date=28 April 2008 |publisher=FindLaw |accessdate=3 October 2012 |archive-date=2012-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120711145149/http://news.findlaw.com/hdocs/docs/spitzer/dupreggw42808cmp.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在2013年，GGW Brands LLC進行以第11章申請破產保護<ref>{{cite web|title=‘Girls Gone Wild’ Files Bankruptcy to Fight Vegas Debt|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-02-28/-girls-gone-wild-files-bankruptcy-to-fight-vegas-debt.html|publisher=Bloomberg|accessdate=28 February 2013|archive-date=2021-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210310235721/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-02-28/-girls-gone-wild-files-bankruptcy-to-fight-vegas-debt.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=FB>{{cite web|last=Egan|first=Matt|title=Legal Headaches Force 'Girls Gone Wild' Into Bankruptcy|url=http://www.foxbusiness.com/industries/2013/03/01/legal-headaches-force-girls-gone-wild-into-bankruptcy/|publisher=Fox Business|accessdate=4-2-2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130304064935/http://www.foxbusiness.com/industries/2013/03/01/legal-headaches-force-girls-gone-wild-into-bankruptcy/|archive-date=2013-03-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。有傳聞指出，[[維維迪娛樂股份有限公司|維維迪娛樂股份有限公司]]進行收購，但未證實<ref>[http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/adult/20131205/00290_003.html AV達人：鹹網破產] {{Wayback|url=http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/adult/20131205/00290_003.html |date=20191117152748 }}[[東方日報|東方日報]] 2013-12-05</REF>。

